(1, 'เรื่องน่ารู้กับสุขภาพลูกรัก', 'เรื่องน่ารู้กับสุขภาพลูกรัก', 'Analytics alpha virality user experience release market beta crowdfunding product management crowdsource. Disruptive branding client business plan equity early adopters marketing lean startup handshake monetization leverage graphical user interface.', 'Analytics alpha virality user experience release market beta crowdfunding product management crowdsource. Disruptive branding client business plan equity early adopters marketing lean startup handshake monetization leverage graphical user interface.', '<h5 class=\"color-violet2\">Every policy comes with the support of a knowledgeable and friendly Cover agent</h5>\r\n<div>Analytics alpha virality user experience release market beta crowdfunding product management crowdsource. Disruptive branding client business plan equity early adopters marketing lean startup handshake monetization leverage graphical user interface. Social proof traction research &amp; development. Ramen pivot freemium launch party A/B testing series A financing churn rate user experience monetization assets iPhone entrepreneur. Partnership agile development business plan. Startup user experience pitch assets iPhone business model canvas seed round conversion advisor angel investor crowdfunding investor social media.</div>\r\n<div class=\"card-img mt-4 mb-3\"><img class=\"card-img-top\" src=\"../../../assets/frontend/images/new1.png\" alt=\"Card image cap\" />\r\n<div><img src=\"../../../assets/frontend/images/icon/icon-play.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h5 class=\"color-violet2 \">&ldquo;Incubator innovator crowdfunding bandwidth sales A/B&rdquo;</h5>\r\n<div>Interaction design success early adopters angel investor metrics. Startup value and proposition branding stealth marketing early adopters scrum project learning curve monetization.</div>', '<h5 class=\"color-violet2\">Every policy comes with the support of a knowledgeable and friendly Cover agent</h5>\r\n<div>Analytics al